<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nevertheless-adv">nevertheless <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌnevəðə'les/    美 /ˌnevərðə'les/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>然而；不过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is little chance that we will win the match. Nevertheless it is important that we try.
我们赢得比赛的可能性不大。不过，重要的是我们要努力争取。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The weather turned bad, but the music festival was a great success nevertheless.
天气变糟了，但是尽管如此，音乐节办得很成功。</p></div></div>